OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774383073
OL,3,CSussex Police detective charged with
OL,4,Cchild sex offences
OL,6,FA detective inspector with Sussex
OL,7,FPolice has been charged with sex
OL,8,Foffences against two children.
OL,10,FIain Macnab has been charged with
OL,11,Fsexual assault, sexual activity with a
OL,12,Fchild and perverting the course of
OL,13,Fjustice.
OL,15,FA Sussex Police spokesman said: "The
OL,16,Fsexual allegations relate to his off-
OL,17,Fduty role as a football coach in West
OL,18,FSussex between October 2024 and
OL,19,FFebruary 2025.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
