PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774383073
OL,3,CSussex Police detective charged with
OL,4,Cchild sex offences
OL,6,F"He was on duty at the time of the
OL,7,Fallegation of perverting the course of
OL,8,Fjustice.
OL,10,F"Both victims and their families are
OL,11,Fbeing supported by specialist officers.
OL,13,F"Macnab was suspended from duty in
OL,14,FMarch 2025 when the reports were first
OL,15,Freceived."
OL,17,FThe 51-year-old, who is based in West
OL,18,FSussex, has been remanded in custody
OL,19,Fto appear at Guildford Magistrates'
OL,20,FCourt later.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
